{"id": "figure_006", "modality": "figures", "name": "Mask R-CNN", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG that reproduces the Mask R-CNN architecture figure. Title 'Mask R-CNN' at top in 32px bold. PIPELINE left-to-right: 'Input Image' -> 'Backbone CNN + FPN' -> 'Region Proposal Network (RPN)' producing 'Region Proposals (RoIs)' -> a 'RoIAlign' box. From RoIAlign the network SPLITS into THREE parallel head branches drawn side by side: (a) a 'Box Regression Head (FC)' producing 'bbox', (b) a 'Classification Head (FC)' producing 'class', (c) a 'Mask Head (FCN)' producing a small 'm x m binary mask' grid (draw a small pixel grid). The three heads must branch from the SAME RoIAlign output node. Annotate the mask branch as a fully-convolutional path distinct from the FC box/class heads. Show the RPN feeding proposals back to RoIAlign. HARDEN (density + alignment): ALSO include (a) a LEGEND box that maps every distinct block color and every arrow/line style used in the figure, and (b) a small tensor-shape annotation on each major block (e.g. 'BxNxd'). Pack the figure densely with at least 14 labeled elements; every group of sibling blocks must be equal-size and share edges, with uniform gutters, and nothing may overlap or clip.", "requirements": ["All components (Input Image, Backbone+FPN, RPN, RoIs, RoIAlign, Box Head, Classification Head, Mask Head, mask grid output) are visible with no clipping at any edge", "No two boxes overlap each other", "Every box label text is fully contained inside its box with no overflow", "Exactly THREE parallel head branches (box, class, mask) all originate from the single RoIAlign output node", "The three head branches do not overlap each other and their connecting arrows do not cross through unrelated boxes", "The Mask Head terminates in a small pixel-grid 'm x m mask' shape that is visibly a grid", "The RPN box connects to RoIAlign via a 'Region Proposals (RoIs)' arrow that does not pass through the backbone box", "The Mask Head is labelled as FCN and the box/class heads are labelled as FC, distinguishing the branches", "The three head branches are evenly spaced / aligned where they run in parallel", "No element is within 10px of any viewport edge", "No horizontal or vertical scrollbar appears; all content fits inside 1920x1080", "A legend box maps every block color and arrow/line style used; each major block carries a tensor-shape annotation; sibling blocks are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters; no element overlaps or is clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 6117, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 5995}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 6312, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 5655}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 0, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 0, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5759, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 1, "rv_total_tokens": 5980}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_006_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_006_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Mask R-CNN Architecture</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        \n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .content {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .main-diagram {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n        \n        .legend {\n            width: 280px;\n            background: white;\n            border: 2px solid #34495e;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            height: fit-content;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-title {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-color {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #333;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-line {\n            width: 30px;\n            height: 2px;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"title\">Mask R-CNN</div>\n        \n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <div class=\"main-diagram\">\n                <svg width=\"1580\" height=\"900\" viewBox=\"0 0 1580 900\">\n                    <!-- Input Image -->\n                    <rect x=\"50\" y=\"200\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"110\" y=\"240\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Input Image</text>\n                    <text x=\"110\" y=\"260\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">H\u00d7W\u00d73</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Backbone CNN + FPN -->\n                    <rect x=\"220\" y=\"180\" width=\"160\" height=\"140\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"300\" y=\"235\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Backbone CNN</text>\n                    <text x=\"300\" y=\"255\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">+ FPN</text>\n                    <text x=\"300\" y=\"275\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">B\u00d7C\u00d7H'\u00d7W'</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- RPN -->\n                    <rect x=\"430\" y=\"120\" width=\"140\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"500\" y=\"150\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Region Proposal</text>\n                    <text x=\"500\" y=\"170\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Network (RPN)</text>\n                    <text x=\"500\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">B\u00d7A\u00d74</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Region Proposals -->\n                    <rect x=\"620\" y=\"120\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"680\" y=\"150\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Region</text>\n                    <text x=\"680\" y=\"165\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Proposals</text>\n                    <text x=\"680\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">(RoIs)</text>\n                    <text x=\"680\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d74</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- RoIAlign -->\n                    <rect x=\"430\" y=\"280\" width=\"140\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#1abc9c\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"500\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">RoIAlign</text>\n                    <text x=\"500\" y=\"340\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d7C\u00d77\u00d77</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Box Regression Head -->\n                    <rect x=\"280\" y=\"450\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#34495e\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"340\" y=\"485\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Box Regression</text>\n                    <text x=\"340\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Head (FC)</text>\n                    <text x=\"340\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d74096\u2192N\u00d74</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Classification Head -->\n                    <rect x=\"430\" y=\"450\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#34495e\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"490\" y=\"485\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Classification</text>\n                    <text x=\"490\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Head (FC)</text>\n                    <text x=\"490\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d74096\u2192N\u00d7K</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Mask Head -->\n                    <rect x=\"580\" y=\"450\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"640\" y=\"485\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Mask Head</text>\n                    <text x=\"640\" y=\"500\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">(FCN)</text>\n                    <text x=\"640\" y=\"525\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d7256\u00d714\u00d714</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Output boxes -->\n                    <!-- BBox output -->\n                    <rect x=\"280\" y=\"600\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"340\" y=\"625\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">bbox</text>\n                    <text x=\"340\" y=\"645\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d74</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Class output -->\n                    <rect x=\"430\" y=\"600\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"490\" y=\"625\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">class</text>\n                    <text x=\"490\" y=\"645\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d7K</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Mask output with grid -->\n                    <rect x=\"580\" y=\"600\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"640\" y=\"620\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"10\" font-weight=\"bold\">m\u00d7m binary mask</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Small pixel grid for mask -->\n                    <g transform=\"translate(615, 630)\">\n                        <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"6\" y=\"0\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"12\" y=\"0\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"18\" y=\"0\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"24\" y=\"0\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"30\" y=\"0\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"36\" y=\"0\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"42\" y=\"0\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        \n                        <rect x=\"0\" y=\"6\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"6\" y=\"6\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"12\" y=\"6\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"18\" y=\"6\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"24\" y=\"6\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"30\" y=\"6\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"36\" y=\"6\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"42\" y=\"6\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                        \n                        <rect x=\"0\" y=\"12\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"6\" y=\"12\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"12\" y=\"12\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"18\" y=\"12\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"24\" y=\"12\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"30\" y=\"12\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"0.5\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"36\" y=\"12\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"42\" y=\"12\" width=\"6\" height=\"6\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                    </g>\n                    <text x=\"640\" y=\"655\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d7m\u00d7m</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Arrows -->\n                    <!-- Input to Backbone -->\n                    <path d=\"M 170 250 L 210 250\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Backbone to RPN -->\n                    <path d=\"M 300 180 L 300 160 L 420 160\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- RPN to Proposals -->\n                    <path d=\"M 570 160 L 610 160\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Backbone to RoIAlign -->\n                    <path d=\"M 380 250 L 420 250 L 420 320 L 430 320\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Proposals to RoIAlign (feedback) -->\n                    <path d=\"M 680 200 L 680 240 L 500 240 L 500 280\" stroke=\"#e74c3c\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- RoIAlign to three heads -->\n                    <path d=\"M 500 360 L 500 400 L 340 400 L 340 450\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 500 360 L 500 450\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 500 360 L 500 400 L 640 400 L 640 450\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Heads to outputs -->\n                    <path d=\"M 340 550 L 340 600\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 490 550 L 490 600\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 640 550 L 640 600\" stroke=\"#27ae60\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Arrow marker definition -->\n                    <defs>\n                        <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                            <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        </marker>\n                    </defs>\n                    \n                    <!-- Annotations -->\n                    <text x=\"750\" y=\"160\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\" font-style=\"italic\">Object Detection</text>\n                    <text x=\"750\" y=\"175\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\" font-style=\"italic\">Proposals</text>\n                    \n                    <text x=\"720\" y=\"400\" fill=\"#27ae60\" font-size=\"11\" font-style=\"italic\" font-weight=\"bold\">Fully Convolutional</text>\n                    <text x=\"720\" y=\"415\" fill=\"#27ae60\" font-size=\"11\" font-style=\"italic\" font-weight=\"bold\">Network (FCN)</text>\n                    \n                    <text x=\"150\" y=\"400\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\" font-style=\"italic\">Fully Connected</text>\n                    <text x=\"150\" y=\"415\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"11\" font-style=\"italic\">Layers (FC)</text>\n                </svg>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"legend\">\n                <div class=\"legend-title\">LEGEND</div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #3498db;\"></div>\n                    <span>Input Layer</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #e74c3c;\"></div>\n                    <span>Feature Extraction</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #9b59b6;\"></div>\n                    <span>Region Proposal</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #f39c12;\"></div>\n                    <span>Proposals/RoIs</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #1abc9c;\"></div>\n                    <span>Feature Alignment</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #34495e;\"></div>\n                    <span>FC Head (Box/Class)</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #27ae60;\"></div>\n                    <span>FCN Head (Mask)</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #ecf0f1;\"></div>\n                    <span>Output</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div style=\"margin: 15px 0; border-top: 1px solid #bdc3c7; padding-top: 10px;\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                        <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: #2c3e50;\"></div>\n                        <span>Data Flow</span>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                        <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: #e74c3c; height: 2px; border-top: 2px dashed #e74c3c; border-bottom: none;\"></div>\n                        <span>Proposal Feedback</span>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                        <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: #27ae60; height: 3px;\"></div>\n                        <span>FCN Path</span>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #bdc3c7; padding-top: 10px;\">\n                    <div style=\"font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 8px;\">Tensor Shapes:</div>\n                    <div style=\"font-size: 10px; line-height: 1.4;\">\n                        B = Batch size<br>\n                        N = Number of RoIs<br>\n                        C = Channels<br>\n                        H,W = Height, Width<br>\n                        A = Anchors per location<br>\n                        K = Number of classes<br>\n                        m = Mask resolution\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Mask R-CNN Architecture</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        \n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n        }\n        \n        .title {\n            font-size: 32px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n        }\n        \n        .content {\n            flex: 1;\n            display: flex;\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n        \n        .main-diagram {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n        \n        .legend {\n            width: 280px;\n            background: white;\n            border: 2px solid #34495e;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            height: fit-content;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-title {\n            font-size: 18px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: #2c3e50;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-item {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 12px;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-color {\n            width: 20px;\n            height: 20px;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #333;\n        }\n        \n        .legend-line {\n            width: 30px;\n            height: 2px;\n            margin-right: 10px;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"title\">Mask R-CNN</div>\n        \n        <div class=\"content\">\n            <div class=\"main-diagram\">\n                <svg width=\"1580\" height=\"900\" viewBox=\"0 0 1580 900\">\n                    <!-- Input Image -->\n                    <rect x=\"50\" y=\"200\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#3498db\" stroke=\"#2980b9\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"110\" y=\"230\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Input Image</text>\n                    <text x=\"110\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">H\u00d7W\u00d73</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Backbone CNN + FPN -->\n                    <rect x=\"220\" y=\"180\" width=\"140\" height=\"120\" fill=\"#e74c3c\" stroke=\"#c0392b\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"290\" y=\"210\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Backbone CNN</text>\n                    <text x=\"290\" y=\"230\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">+ FPN</text>\n                    <text x=\"290\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">Feature Maps</text>\n                    <text x=\"290\" y=\"270\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">H/k\u00d7W/k\u00d7C</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- RPN -->\n                    <rect x=\"410\" y=\"120\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#9b59b6\" stroke=\"#8e44ad\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"470\" y=\"145\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Region</text>\n                    <text x=\"470\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Proposal</text>\n                    <text x=\"470\" y=\"175\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Network</text>\n                    <text x=\"470\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">(RPN)</text>\n                    <text x=\"470\" y=\"205\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d74</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Region Proposals -->\n                    <rect x=\"580\" y=\"140\" width=\"120\" height=\"60\" fill=\"#f39c12\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"640\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Region</text>\n                    <text x=\"640\" y=\"175\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Proposals</text>\n                    <text x=\"640\" y=\"190\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d74 (RoIs)</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- RoIAlign -->\n                    <rect x=\"410\" y=\"280\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#1abc9c\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"470\" y=\"310\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">RoIAlign</text>\n                    <text x=\"470\" y=\"330\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">7\u00d77\u00d7C</text>\n                    <text x=\"470\" y=\"345\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">per RoI</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Box Regression Head -->\n                    <rect x=\"600\" y=\"380\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#34495e\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Box</text>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Regression</text>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"435\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Head (FC)</text>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"455\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">FC Layers</text>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"470\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d74</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Classification Head -->\n                    <rect x=\"750\" y=\"380\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#34495e\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"810\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Classification</text>\n                    <text x=\"810\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Head (FC)</text>\n                    <text x=\"810\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">FC Layers</text>\n                    <text x=\"810\" y=\"455\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d7K classes</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Mask Head -->\n                    <rect x=\"900\" y=\"380\" width=\"120\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#27ae60\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"960\" y=\"405\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">Mask Head</text>\n                    <text x=\"960\" y=\"420\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">(FCN)</text>\n                    <text x=\"960\" y=\"440\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">Conv Layers</text>\n                    <text x=\"960\" y=\"455\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"white\" font-size=\"10\">N\u00d7K\u00d7m\u00d7m</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Output boxes -->\n                    <rect x=\"600\" y=\"520\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"660\" y=\"545\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">bbox</text>\n                    \n                    <rect x=\"750\" y=\"520\" width=\"120\" height=\"40\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"810\" y=\"545\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">class</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Mask output with grid -->\n                    <rect x=\"900\" y=\"520\" width=\"120\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"5\"/>\n                    <text x=\"960\" y=\"540\" text-anchor=\"middle\" fill=\"#2c3e50\" font-size=\"12\" font-weight=\"bold\">m\u00d7m binary mask</text>\n                    \n                    <!-- Small pixel grid -->\n                    <g transform=\"translate(930, 550)\">\n                        <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"8\" y=\"0\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"16\" y=\"0\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"24\" y=\"0\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"32\" y=\"0\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"40\" y=\"0\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"48\" y=\"0\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"56\" y=\"0\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        \n                        <rect x=\"0\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"8\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"16\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"24\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"32\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"40\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"48\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"56\" y=\"8\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\"/>\n                        \n                        <rect x=\"0\" y=\"16\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"8\" y=\"16\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"16\" y=\"16\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"24\" y=\"16\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"32\" y=\"16\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"40\" y=\"16\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#ecf0f1\" stroke=\"#bdc3c7\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"48\" y=\"16\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        <rect x=\"56\" y=\"16\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                    </g>\n                    \n                    <!-- Arrows -->\n                    <!-- Input to Backbone -->\n                    <path d=\"M 170 240 L 210 240\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Backbone to RPN -->\n                    <path d=\"M 290 180 L 290 150 L 400 150 L 400 170\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- RPN to Proposals -->\n                    <path d=\"M 530 170 L 570 170\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Backbone to RoIAlign -->\n                    <path d=\"M 360 240 L 380 240 L 380 320 L 400 320\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Proposals to RoIAlign -->\n                    <path d=\"M 640 200 L 640 250 L 520 250 L 520 270\" stroke=\"#e67e22\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- RoIAlign to three heads -->\n                    <path d=\"M 530 320 L 590 320 L 590 430\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 530 320 L 740 320 L 740 430\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 530 320 L 890 320 L 890 430\" stroke=\"#16a085\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Heads to outputs -->\n                    <path d=\"M 660 480 L 660 510\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 810 480 L 810 510\" stroke=\"#2c3e50\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    <path d=\"M 960 480 L 960 510\" stroke=\"#229954\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n                    \n                    <!-- Arrow marker definition -->\n                    <defs>\n                        <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                            <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2c3e50\"/>\n                        </marker>\n                    </defs>\n                    \n                    <!-- Annotations -->\n                    <text x=\"1050\" y=\"350\" fill=\"#27ae60\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Fully Convolutional</text>\n                    <text x=\"1050\" y=\"365\" fill=\"#27ae60\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Network (FCN)</text>\n                    \n                    <text x=\"1050\" y=\"400\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Fully Connected</text>\n                    <text x=\"1050\" y=\"415\" fill=\"#34495e\" font-size=\"11\" font-weight=\"bold\">Layers (FC)</text>\n                </svg>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"legend\">\n                <div class=\"legend-title\">LEGEND</div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #3498db;\"></div>\n                    <span>Input Layer</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #e74c3c;\"></div>\n                    <span>Feature Extraction</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #9b59b6;\"></div>\n                    <span>Region Proposal</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #f39c12;\"></div>\n                    <span>Proposals/RoIs</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #1abc9c;\"></div>\n                    <span>RoI Processing</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #34495e;\"></div>\n                    <span>FC Head (Box/Class)</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #27ae60;\"></div>\n                    <span>FCN Head (Mask)</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-color\" style=\"background: #ecf0f1;\"></div>\n                    <span>Output</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: #2c3e50;\"></div>\n                    <span>Data Flow</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: #e67e22; height: 3px; background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, #e67e22 0px, #e67e22 5px, transparent 5px, transparent 10px);\"></div>\n                    <span>RoI Proposals</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: #16a085;\"></div>\n                    <span>RoIAlign Output</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div class=\"legend-item\">\n                    <div class=\"legend-line\" style=\"background: #229954;\"></div>\n                    <span>Mask Branch</span>\n                </div>\n                \n                <div style=\"margin-top: 20px; font-size: 11px; color: #7f8c8d;\">\n                    <div><strong>Tensor Shapes:</strong></div>\n                    <div>H\u00d7W\u00d73: Input dimensions</div>\n                    <div>N\u00d74: N proposals, 4 coords</div>\n                    <div>N\u00d7K: N objects, K classes</div>\n                    <div>m\u00d7m: Mask resolution</div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}